{"type": "article", "id": 10440, "title": "Christian Sjostrom 烟灰缸", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-05T07:14:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235923c2oWyOCN8IRrpK6V.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">6 月 1 日北京禁烟令正式开始实施，不知道您怎么看待这个“史上最严禁烟令”。这是 Christian Sjostrom 设计的一个烟灰缸，“骷髅头”这个常常在禁烟宣传里面出现的意象这次出现在了他的烟灰缸中，骷髅头的“眼睛”用来弹烟灰，而“牙齿”则是倾倒烟灰的出口，黑色幽默里面包含了对“禁烟”的态度。虽然有点老套，但用来激励戒烟，或许能有一点点作用。<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/ash-tray-skully-06-04-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235921NbU4ZvRQC9yzdwcO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235921wAfoRl64jbL5J9EX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523592275wtMGmDpHIkVEaX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.85574572\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235922GKJUadZihwC2InrR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.85574572\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235922XResPAjQOF53Nf27.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.85574572\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}